    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>主题曲演唱：Marnée Richardson，词曲创作与制作：Elvisish​</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >布莱斯方块：等距推箱解谜之旅！亮点速览：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 经典玩法传承：灵感源于《拯救巡逻兵》《波洛冒险》《谜题深渊》《罗罗大冒险》及《斯奎迪船长的推箱密航》！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 主线百关征程 + 30个特别行动关卡，更藏有秘密世界与多重结局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 亦正亦邪的主角：实用主义至上的小机灵鬼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 独创氛围电子乐：虚拟模拟合成器打造沉浸声境！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Windows平台丝滑体验：165fps+超流畅动态，现代画质渲染！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 彩蛋致敬90年代：游戏秘档与音乐回忆杀！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 数十种仓库番式机制与玩法设计！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 10+独特敌人潜伏暗处！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 新奇关卡结构！路径追踪敌兵！环境动态陷阱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 支持12种语言！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 内置完整关卡编辑器、战役制作器及 Steam™ Workshop® 上传工具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 秘密世界、隐藏模式、终极Boss与分支结局待你解锁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/6ef9f7b38d08c2fcfc12253b2dc8dd50.poster.avif?t=1767382528\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/6ef9f7b38d08c2fcfc12253b2dc8dd50.webm?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/6ef9f7b38d08c2fcfc12253b2dc8dd50.mp4?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可曾渴望推箱开路，步步为营？滑移入位，绝境求生？穿梭于斑斓的等距瓦片空间，畅游预渲染视效与酷炫卡通角色的世界？布莱斯方块，终极之选！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/5d01e02f9988d6d783ee89fa39f91530.avif?t=1767382528\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备迎接推箱盛宴！《布莱斯方块》是一款延续MSDOSWare风格的后千禧年游戏！布莱斯在‘一键通关魔盒’中发现新的时空裂隙，再度穿越至25年前——纳什执掌EuroMaxi K&amp;C的黄金年代！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在纯粹的等距迈耶式世界中，推箱、滑行、泅渡、奔逃、滚球，跨越130+怀旧关卡，收集散落的乐器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操纵你的小人来回推箱...从未如此简单！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/0f54fc0f6a0a8d5c0a0d92fcb38b056d.poster.avif?t=1767382528\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/0f54fc0f6a0a8d5c0a0d92fcb38b056d.webm?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/0f54fc0f6a0a8d5c0a0d92fcb38b056d.mp4?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上、下、左、右，直向移动（无斜向！），攻克险要地形，力求速通或极简操作！​​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/f6bf131a58562dc747a5de738a25cb70.avif?t=1767382528\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推箱之旅危机四伏：流沙陷足、静水深流、激流险滩、移形地砖、滑溜冰面、灼热炭火！​​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/c78563594f82a78fb0b97af7ef8fb9e7.poster.avif?t=1767382528\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/c78563594f82a78fb0b97af7ef8fb9e7.webm?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/c78563594f82a78fb0b97af7ef8fb9e7.mp4?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精打细算，因地制宜！​​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/9f5bbe1d76113743c6ace235996171f6.avif?t=1767382528\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >滚球（提示：永远不会停歇！）、暴躁斯克伦普™、激光束（需镜面反射... 哈！各位老玩家都懂灵感来源~） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/5c4f483213cd19673cbcc066a7f7b0d1.poster.avif?t=1767382528\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/5c4f483213cd19673cbcc066a7f7b0d1.webm?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/5c4f483213cd19673cbcc066a7f7b0d1.mp4?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >锁闭门扉、压力踏板...机关算尽只为迷惑你，但你终将智胜一筹！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/defe12b19e66c7cddba28aa5c107c27d.avif?t=1767382528\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机关算尽、烧脑谜题、沉浸数小时，预渲染视效构筑绝美世界！​​ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/30ef776be0647245bf18b62f1455b550.poster.avif?t=1767382528\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/30ef776be0647245bf18b62f1455b550.webm?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/30ef776be0647245bf18b62f1455b550.mp4?t=1767382528\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世间仅此一款《布莱斯方块》！↓↓↓​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144990/extras/0ef8e2f8645dddfa1511262fa03a6ce0.avif?t=1767382528\" width=800 height=718 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>主题曲演唱：Marnée Richardson（ </i><br><br><br><br><br>在《布莱斯方块》的创作过程中，包括主题音乐、游戏配乐、美术设计及所有其他环节，均绝无使用AI技术</p>",
